dct_title_s: South America, west coast, sheet XVIII : Ecuador, Ayangui Pt. to Verde Pt.
dct_description_sm: "Published according to Act of Parliament ... Sepr. 29th. 1847. Corrections to 1861." Covers the coast of northwestern Ecuador, chiefly in Esmeraldas and Manabí Provinces. Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. Insets: Cape Parado anchorage -- Manta Bay. "1814"--Lower right margin.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty : Sold by J.D. Potter, agent for the Admiralty charts, 1861.
